        <h2>About Kidangoor</h2>
        <p>Kidangoor is a beautiful town near Pala in Kottayam, Kerala, filled with lush greenery, scenic landscapes, and rich cultural heritage. It is known for its warm people and vibrant traditions.</p>
        
        <h2>Famous Attractions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Kidangoor Subramanya Swami Temple</li>
            <li>Scenic Waterways and Green Fields</li>
            <li>Historic Landmarks</li>
            <li>Traditional Markets</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Local Cuisine</h2>
        <p>The local cuisine is a blend of spicy, sweet, and savory flavors. Must-try dishes include traditional Kerala meals, seafood specialties, and delicious desserts.</p>
        
